{"tid":616518,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 宣佈：由Chrome 68 開始，所有http網站均顯示為「不安全」","createTime":"2018-04-04T08:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T09:29:18.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9df6cf9dcaeb39fcd70570967f7f47b378b91b57","tid":616518,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://blog.chromium.org/2018/02/a-secure-web-is-here-to-stay.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.chromium.org%2F2018%2F02%2Fa-secure-web-is-here-to-stay.html%3Fm%3D1&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=c485e238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.chromium.org/2018/02/a-secure-web-is-here-to-stay.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/02/14/chrome-will-mark-all-http-sites-as-not-secure-starting-in-july/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2Fchrome-will-mark-all-http-sites-as-not-secure-starting-in-july%2F&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=4b1e0df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/02/14/chrome-will-mark-all-http-sites-as-not-secure-starting-in-july/</a><br />\n<br />\nIT人注意啦<br />\n<br />\n如果閣下的網頁，仲係得http連線，而非https連線，由chrome 68開始就會被顯示做「不安全」連線。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 預計 Chrome 68 將在2018年7月左右推出。<br />\n<br />\n即使係純粹 information portal, 或只係information delivery only website，都要https 加密<br />\n<br />\n如果閣下的網站，唔想再有不安全標示，請盡快向 certificate authority購買數碼證書，以https運作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nhttps網頁有以下好處<br />\n<br />\n1 確保網站受核證機構verify過，防止釣魚網站<br />\n<br />\n2 確保中間人唔會加入或修改信息"},{"pid":"637475c2dcdf6c78da71f919256dc5dba0a833f1","tid":616518,"uid":36120,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"攪到咁煩膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294eb8d317b1bf4938c200b3269b746ac9a26194","tid":616518,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dis